{"word":"G4408 - πρῶρα - prōra - pro'-ra - Forepart","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πρῶρα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">prōra</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pro'-ra</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Forepart</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முன்னணியம் - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"the prow or forward part of a ship"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Feminine of a presumed derivation of <a href=\"#/G4253 - πρό - pró - pro/4253\">G4253</a> as noun; the <i>prow</i>, that is, forward part of a vessel: - forepart (-ship).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}